{"type": "article", "id": 21891, "title": "这个设计了不起之“巴黎家居装饰博览会”", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-02-04T07:30:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 23137, "name": "巴黎家居博览会"}, {"id": 23138, "name": "Maison&Objet"}, {"id": 23139, "name": "valerie objects"}, {"id": 23140, "name": "pinch"}, {"id": 23141, "name": "LA BOITE"}, {"id": 23142, "name": "samuel accoceberry"}, {"id": 20154, "name": "Elena Salmistraro"}, {"id": 23143, "name": "ander lizaso"}, {"id": 23144, "name": "jean louis iratzoki"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 70, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607154018pdB7UMHhEbFnmYvu.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>“the cutlery project” by valerie objects</h2>\n<p>比利时的一家新品牌 valerie_objects 在巴黎家具博览会上推出了一套餐具项目，他们邀请多位设计师重新设计这些生活中常见的餐具。日本设计师二俣公一（koichi futatsumata）将手柄设计成凸出的八角形，两端连接依然是片状的，有雕塑感。 wieki somers工作室的餐具手柄是中空的，像是将金属折叠起来。荷兰设计师 maarten baas 则走向精致的反面，餐具的形状更随意，尤其是切刀的刀口并不规整，增加了一份天然和自在。<a href=\"http://www.valerie-objects.com/Product/The_Cutlery_Project/\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154002gBGpy93VF25CrZKj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154002jHbphQ1MzIxnRsF7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154003IQ2MvqXE3JAF1rVZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154003hXePMolm6OxSVbK5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154003e4ixO50jVG3UBaRr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77506112\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154004sXLZPvkU8lQIxea0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76894866\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>paleta &amp; concha by samuel accoceberry </h2>\n<p>巴黎设计师 samuel accoceberry  带来了一组扶手椅和沙发，都接近北欧的极简风格，用橡木或者胡桃木搭配彩色的垫子。扶手椅 paleta 的名字是一种球拍，扶手的形状与球拍类似。而 concha 在西班牙语中是贝壳的意思，沙发就有像贝壳一样旋转和半包围的形状，明亮的黄色让它具有热情的特征。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154005rYSu6jxGJyHzEDMI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.98777506\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154005OCY4Dnlyo7R1mQq3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154006uiJ8GZzqBw6DvYL3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62469438\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154006Djfr1BeX9cLKlIu5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.88264059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071540078QVb4zPxZ0wUrSXp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8594132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>“nim”&amp;“leta”&amp;“imo”by pinch</h2>\n<p>这套家具系列来自伦敦的设计工作室 pinch，他们使用了天然的材料。咖啡桌的表面近似大理石，最下面是深灰色的，混合了蓝色和土黄色，慢慢渐变到了白色，很有雕塑感。这种雕塑感延续到了躺椅，像是一个人侧卧着。而折叠凳 imo 则更具实用性，它可以挂在墙上，不同的木材对应了不同的颜色和质感，其中限量的绿色使用了冷衫，非常亮丽。<a href=\"http://pinchdesign.com/products/nim\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154007RXD4Swgoy31dikWM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72127139\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154008knFzBTeuGaY5yxK7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68215159\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154008QUEtRr8JFqiPW0H2.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65281174\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154009FZxNMIoc1kp78hWu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80317848\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154010WgMUf3jZ8QLvl2h0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75550122\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>“LP160” by LA BOITE</h2>\n<p>法国高端音响生产商 LA BOITE 在家博会上发布了一款多功能扬声器，有点类似老式的录音机，他们希望能播放任何形式的音源。打开盖子后是一款留声机，也可以放 CD，通过蓝牙连接上智能设备。音质上，由电音博士 yvon maurel 和 R&amp;D 实验室一起实验，偏细腻。扬声器是用橡木和铝合金材质制作，高度正好是一个小桌子，可以当做书桌台。<a href=\"http://laboiteconcept.com/en/lp-160-home.php\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154010R6kyjSLX5rEAJaK3.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154011amgAZ0NYCqXwPGzQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7408313\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071540118XxbA7kiBDsOPGCn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74938875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154012aNYSUMWXxDlyZi8e.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154013GntThKQSk7se5y64.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>“ensemble” by elena salmistraro</h2>\n<p>玻璃的艺术表现是常常被设计师开发，意大利设计师 elena salmistraro 带来了一组玻璃容器就发挥了玻璃的重叠效果。它的外形有点像一盏小灯，有带菱形纹路的圆锥形底座和灯笼似的灯罩，中间空出了一根细长的玻璃柱，从上至下，和透明与半透明的玻璃外壳重叠，形成了三种不同的效果，有层次感。它可以用来当做花瓶使用。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071540139ZHwPlW3AcINpiyx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.14914425\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154014oaxvR35nDT4XhVc1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154014q2EGCJrdW9VfUetl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154015d0p9uxHQl21WDocy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33374083\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>“zumitz”系列 by jean louis iratzoki&amp;ander lizaso</h2>\n<p>西班牙设计师 jean louis iratzoki 和 ander lizaso 一起推出了这套编织家具，这种用栗树条的编织工艺正是巴斯克人的特色。栗树条宽而结实，再用金属框做支撑，可以运用在咖啡桌、屏风、花篮等承重要求较小的地方，很亲切，也是延续传统手艺的方式。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154015MYyoz6L4lDx7aCnr.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73594132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154016pLv3TxhYUwoGrFO0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73594132\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154016WfKNlTdAi5CxHPD7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.80929095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607154017wjImVhtTCibKOQ58.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.30317848\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071540187SLgwWHil5R4usTK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57334963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}